        </table>
        <p><em>* Private repositories require authentication as the owner.</em></p>

        <h3>Create repository</h3>
        <pre><code>POST /api/repos
{
  "name": "my-project",
  "description": "Optional description",
  "is_private": false,
  "website": "https://example.com"
}</code></pre>

        <h3>Commit format</h3>
        <pre><code>GET /api/repos/alice/myrepo/commits/main

→ [
  {
    "hash": "abc1234...",
    "shortHash": "abc1234",
    "message": "Add feature X",
    "author": "Alice",
    "email": "alice@example.com",
    "date": "2026-06-07T10:00:00+09:00"
  }
]</code></pre>
      </section>

